{"id":2800,"date":"2025-03-03T07:29:45","date_gmt":"2025-03-03T07:29:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/?page_id=2800"},"modified":"2025-03-03T07:54:16","modified_gmt":"2025-03-03T07:54:16","slug":"church-and-union-restaurant-construction","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/hoodbuilders-featured-projects\/church-and-union-restaurant-construction\/","title":{"rendered":"Church And Union"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<p>2024 Modern Restaurant Comprehensive Project<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This project stands as one of HoodBuilder\u2019s most notable achievements in 2024, successfully completed from January to September 2024. The primary goal was the full design and execution of a modern restaurant equipped with all necessary functionalities, delivered within an approximate budget of $1.2 million. Our team leveraged years of expertise and experience to provide all required services for this project while adhering to the highest standards of quality and safety.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Key Project Details:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Duration: January to September 2024 (9 months)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Total Cost: Approximately $1.2 million<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scope of Services: The project encompassed all of our specialized services, including:\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Complete restaurant design and construction (Restaurant Construction)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Installation of heating, cooling, and ventilation systems (HVAC Installation)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Installation of industrial hoods and ventilation fans (Hood Fan Installation)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Design and implementation of hood fire suppression systems (Hood Fire Suppression)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Installation of fire sprinkler systems (Fire Sprinkler Installation)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Implementation of advanced fire alarm systems (Fire Alarm Installation)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With a keen focus on detail and compliance with safety and quality standards, we successfully created a safe, efficient, and aesthetically pleasing space that met the clien<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2801\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction-rotated.jpg 1512w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction2-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2802\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction2-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Restaurant-Construction2-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder